{"tid":1171293,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"神戶勝利船2年半合約邀雲加接手","createTime":"2019-05-25T15:08:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-26T09:11:19.000Z","uid":164771,"like":47,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"008b43dbf0e343720bdafbdc3917d3513a276d58","tid":1171293,"uid":164771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T15:08:20.000Z","msg":"雲加自2018年夏天離開阿仙奴後雖表明無意退休，但一直未有新工作的他曾與多支球隊扯上關係，近日亦有消息指神戶勝利船已正式向他招手，期望他可復出領軍，帶領陣中的恩尼斯達、韋拿及普多斯基等一班球星。<br />\n<br />\n報道指神戶勝利船開出一紙2年半年薪達400萬歐元的合約，由於雲加曾執教名古屋八鯨，懂得日語及多國語言的他將不成問題，現在只等他肯首接掌球隊。<br />\n<br />\n事實上「教授」早已表明他將回到球壇工作，不論是否再當教練，都必定和足球十分接近。"},{"pid":"ffc619a4269574b3ac79f13b085c2651d839f204","tid":1171293,"uid":97212,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T15:09:11.000Z","msg":"爺爺識日文<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屈到"},{"pid":"e2100d3a5baeaa7ad57c4026ac823967ac786f92","tid":1171293,"uid":171399,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"quote":{"pid":"ffc619a4269574b3ac79f13b085c2651d839f204","tid":1171293,"uid":97212,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T15:09:11.000Z","msg":"爺爺識日文<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屈到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T15:12:01.000Z","msg":"佢之前教過名古屋鯨魚"},{"pid":"62f2213da6f9662f4f3e13c90107385d48b542cd","tid":1171293,"uid":253829,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T15:21:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/iKdIgwR2VuU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FiKdIgwR2VuU&d=mZhSvp2BRS%2BtHw05K%2FyMFKnyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=6ed7181b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/iKdIgwR2VuU</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}